title: Hainan Starts World's Largest Free Trade Zone Construction at its 30-year-old Birthday
description:
Year 2018 marks the 30th anniversary of the establishment of Hainan province and Hainan special economic zone. 

In 2018, The CPC Central Committee has decided to support Hainan in building the whole island into a pilot free trade zone, gradually exploring and steadily promoting the establishment of a free trade port with Chinese characteristics, and promulgating policies and institutional systems for the free trade port step by step and in stages.
